{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cradle of Nightmares: Flowers to You is an ATB turn-based game based on combat adventures made by RPGMaker.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Players will play as a high school student named Le Qing, as the world is being torn apart by a mysterious phenomenon from outside the world, the &quot;White Light&quot;, and you will start from the ordinary daily life and fall into the dark and gloomy &quot;Second World&quot;, where you will embark on a journey to find your best friends, fight against the madmen under the invasion of emptiness, and finally end the filthy fate of mankind.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>~Fall into darkness at the moment~</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>- Soul-mimicking gameplay system</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>With the &quot;flower basket&quot; as the node, the map exploration is carried out in a propulsive manner, as well as the appropriate shortcut and regional connectivity design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>In battle, accumulate special skills with basic attack/defense/skills, and release strong attack skills to turn the tide</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The main and secondary hands cooperate with the strike, the attribute restraint of spells, the backstab system, etc</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/\u201c\u82b1\u7bee\u201d\u7684\u8282\u70b9\u4f20\u9001\u529f\u80fd.gif?t=1739590116\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>~Thoughts converge into light~</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>- Rich weapon skill design</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>A skill set with 2~5 skills as a weapon, rich loadout slots, off-hands, and spells</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>- Turn-based but unique battle mode</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The enemy/player swing back and forth design reduces the unpredictability of the traditional turn-based system and strengthens the player's sense of grasp of the battle</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/\u201c\u80cc\u523a\u201d\u7cfb\u7edf\u4e0e\u754c\u9762\u5c55\u793a.gif?t=1739590116\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>~Ran, I am a round of the sun~</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>- Quite a wealth of maps, enemies, and boss battles to meet players' expectations for map exploration and fighting against strong enemies</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Plenty of plot and NPC side quests</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Special NPC frenzy battles</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiple endings, multi-week inherited gameplay, and difficulty increases in the process</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/\u7cbe\u82f1\u654c\u4eba\u4e0e\u6218\u6597\u5c55\u793a.gif?t=1739590116\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3469850/extras/BOSS\u6218\u5c55\u793a.gif?t=1739590116\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"\u9634\u973e\u6682\u9690","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3469850/6ea7aff4cb540ffb2e2c5780eb805e54fa2d54ef.jpg"},{"name":"\u82b1\u5f00\u82b1\u8c22","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3469850/6ea7aff4cb540ffb2e2c5780eb805e54fa2d54ef.jpg"},{"name":"\u8bf7\u4f60\u53bb\u6b7b\uff01","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3469850/6ea7aff4cb540ffb2e2c5780eb805e54fa2d54ef.jpg"},{"name":"\u6708\u5149\u7834\u788e","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunit